{
  "stem": "14060.9",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I noticed that one of my trips, as I was coming back from the Budapest, I come at the station where I just walk out, you know.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "This guy comes to me, identify yourself.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I look at him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I say, what do you want?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He said, identify yourself.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he shows me he's from the security police.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So at that time they started checking the people who were arriving already on the border towns.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, that was that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I told you my lovely experience of Mr.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Cardinal Mindszenty's speech earlier, I think.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in April, after Pesach, 1949, I decided that Hungary and I will part company.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't like them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They didn't do us many favors.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I certainly wasn't interested to come under a Communist-dominated era where Jews were also considered as unreliable, capitalist, bourgeois, whatever names they fancied to give.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I escaped one Sunday afternoon.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I went out-- I paid $100, which was quite a lot of money in those days, to a guy who owned a grape plantation on both sides of the border.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You know, vine-- vineyards.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the-- the barbed wires were there already.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I could describe it-- two sets of wire by one and a half meter high, cross and [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Anyway, but it wasn't mined.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I went out with a-- from a comfortable home with everything left behind except what I managed to send ahead-- some silver and Persian carpets and whatnot, so a few belongings, which I got back very few, after the war-- which I sent out.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I paid a lot of money for somebody who was probably not worth it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we-- I arrived there on the auspices that I went out to play ping-pong.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
